00:19:36.180 --> 00:19:43.080
My question is, since design can be so subjective, how
do you decide whether or not a design idea works?

00:19:43.580 --> 00:19:47.620
Is it based on your individual process or
based on feedback after the fact?

00:19:47.620 --> 00:19:51.010
Also, how did you hone your
