00:24:36.240 --> 00:24:40.690
exhilarating and incredibly exhilarating to
figure out how to solve that problem with

00:24:40.690 --> 00:24:42.250
Robert Gober.

00:24:42.250 --> 00:24:44.750
So, yeah.

00:24:44.750 --> 00:24:48.180
I would say that the challenges
are really exciting as well.

00:24:48.180 --> 00:24:50.550
